00:01:31.220 --> 00:01:33.260
After mixing it 

00:01:33.420 --> 00:01:37.720
apply it in your hairs like you apply oil from root

00:01:37.980 --> 00:01:39.440
then leave for an hour

00:01:40.540 --> 00:01:45.900
When it starts drying,you will feel your hairs are very dry and rough

00:01:45.900 --> 00:01:49.100
your hairs are very lumpy 

00:01:49.700 --> 00:01:52.980
